[22/07/2026 09:38:34] [Erika] [credenciamento@ciscai.com.br] X is the imap foldername you have to use in command line options and
[22/07/2026 09:38:34] [Erika] [credenciamento@ciscai.com.br] Y is the utf8 output just printed for convenience, to recognize it.
